  &END

  &POTENTIAL
    PSEUDO_TYPE GTH
    &GTH_POTENTIAL
    2    2    0    0
    0.33842037096913       2   -8.80041712690571    1.33249221738633
       1
    0.30268766321861       1    9.60946227253083
    &END
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0
  &END POTENTIAL
  &POWELL
      ACCURACY   1.e-14
      STEP_SIZE  0.20
  &END

&END ATOM
